TRIAGE MODEL (RandomForest):
â”œâ”€ Input Features:
â”‚  â”œâ”€ age (0-120)
â”‚  â”œâ”€ heart_rate (40-200 bpm)
â”‚  â”œâ”€ bp_systolic (50-250 mmHg)
â”‚  â”œâ”€ bp_diastolic (30-150 mmHg)
