This architectural documentation provides a complete technical reference for:
- System design and components
- Data flow and processing
- Database structure
- Security implementation
- AI/ML integration
- Deployment topology
- Mobile architecture
- External integrations
- Monitoring strategy

All components work together to create a secure, scalable, HIPAA-compliant
emergency healthcare communication platform.